name: Tiki (Adult) (Fire Emblem: Awakening) LoRA
description:
Tiki from Fire Emblem: Awakening, trained on animefull.

Around 0.8 weight works well. Trigger word is 'tiki fe'.

Really happy with how this one turned out. Though, I included a bunch of images of her Heroes brave alt in the dataset, but unfortunately it doesn't handle that very well. Still, the other results are awesome other than the occasional weird looking tiara. It also usually misses her boots without 'red thigh boots' in the prompt.
